node.text:
For the Haute Couture FW2021-22 collection, Chitose Abe runs the @jeanpaulgaultier  universe through the sacai filter with 31 looks. This collection is in line with the new collaborative era, inviting other guests like tattoo artist @_dr_woo_ , shoe designer @pierrehardy and @nike .
 
#JeanPaulGaultier #Sacai #scaiofficial #GaultierParis

node.title: Gaultier Paris by Sacai / HC FW2021-22

node.text:
sacai 2021 Autumn & Winter collection

#sacai #sacaiofficial 

Designer / Chitose Abe
Creative direction / sacai and Daisuke Gemma @daisukeg 
Styling and Creative direction / Karl Templer at Camilla Johnson-Hill
Hair stylist/ ASASHI(OTA OFFICE) @asashihair 
Makeup / Yuka Washizu(beauty direction) @yuka_washizu 
Music / Yu Su @yusu_suyu 
Director of Photography / Shoji Uchida

Director / Yuichi Kodama　
Assistant Director / Jeffrey Stockwell / Reggie White
Lighting Director / Akifumi Yonei
1st Camera Assistant / Yuji Okabe
1st Light Assistant / Miyuki Kawajiri
Key Grip / O.F Inc.
Drone OP / Toshikazu Kazama
DIT / Atsumasa Kachi
Art Designer / Toshihide Sakai
 
Offline Editor / Yuichi Kodama / Gorilla
Online Editor / Yusuke Yamazaki
VFX Supervisor / Masashi Kuwahara（VISUALMAN TOKYO）
CG Production Manager / Takahiro Makino（VISUALMAN TOKYO）

Colorist / Brandon Chaves (incolor)
Mixer / Kazune Masutomi
Sound Effector / Yoshiaki Tokunaga

Production / GEEK PICTURES 
Producer/ Mamoru Inagaki / Mizuki Ohno
Production Manager / Yosuke Mimori / Takehiro Yaegashi

Project partner
Contents director / Takeshi Ishida
Executive producer / Ryota Fujima

Special thanks / KDDI CORPORATION

node.text:
⠀

LOVE OVER RULES ⠀⠀
⠀⠀
In collaboration with artist @hankwillisthomas, sacai's 2021 Pre Spring collection and Men's Spring & Summer collection celebrates those who have broken the rules to defy society’s expectations, regardless of race, culture or gender. ⠀⠀
⠀⠀
The campaign realized by Hank Willis Thomas Studio in collaboration with Equator Productions, features trumpeter and composer Keyon Harrold; movement artist, Mizuho Kappa; artist, Zoë Buckman; designer and advocate, Céline Semaan Vernon; jazz pianist, Jason Moran; and artist and activist, Chella Man; as well as Thomas himself and wife, curator Rujeko Hockley. ⠀⠀
⠀
ハンク・ウィリス・トーマス@hankwillisthomasとのコラボレーションにより、sacai 2021 Pre Spring collection and Men's Spring & Summer collectionは、人種や文化、性別に関係なく、既存のルールや境界線を超えてきた人々を、Hank Willis Thomasが実現したキャ ンペーンを通じて称える。⠀
⠀
ハンク・ウィリス・トーマス・スタジオがエクエーター・プロダクションズとのコラボレーションで実現したこのキャンペーンには、トランペット奏者で作曲家のキーヨン・ハロルド、ムーブメント・アーティストのミズホ・カッパ、アーティストのゾエ・バックマン、デザイナーであり提唱者でもあるセリーヌ・セマーン・ヴァーノン、ジャズ・ピアニストのジェーソン・モラン、アーティストでありアクティビストでもあるチェラ・マン、そしてトーマス本人と妻でキュレーターのルジェコ・ホックリーが参加している。⠀
⠀
⠀⠀
#LOVEOVERRULES #HANKWILLISTHOMAS @hankwillisthomas ⠀
@sacaiofficial 
#SACAI #SACAIOFFICIAL⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Creative Director: Albert James Ignacio @totallywithit⠀⠀
Executive Producer: Fiana Keleta @fianakeleta⠀⠀
Producer: Christina Caputo @caputz⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Film in Partnership with: @equatorproductions⠀⠀
Co-Directors: Anthony Prince Leslie @anthonyprinceleslie + Ashley Cimone @ashleycimone⠀⠀
DP: Ryan Chun @6corners ⠀⠀
Composer: Keyon Harrold @keyonharrold⠀⠀
Movement Artist: Mizuho Kappa @mizup0i_kappa⠀⠀
Producer - Ché Nembhard- @mindofmymind⠀⠀
Hair- Anike Rabiu - @anikerabiu⠀⠀
Makeup- Mimi Quiquine - @@mimiquiquine⠀⠀
Styled by: Ade Samuel @adesamuel⠀⠀
Stylist Assistant- Ricchara Pina - @rixz⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Available now in stores.

node.text:
Nike x sacai x CLOT LDWaffle

Nike x sacai x CLOT LDWaffle will be released on Thursday, September 9th.
Launch will feature NET/ORANGE BLAZE-DP RED-GRN BN colorway.
Raffle for sacai will take place only at sacai online store, https://store.sacai.jp/
Raffle starts at 19:00pm on September 6th, and closes at 7:00AM September 7th.
sacai x CLOT collaboration will also launch RTW capsule collection, exclusively at sacai THE store.
 
Please submit raffle entry from the Nike x sacai x CLOT LDWaffle product page that will be shown starting on September 6th starting 19:00 pm till 7:00 am next day, September 7th.
★Only one pair of either color is valid for raffle entry. Visit the raffle page for more instructions.
https://store.sacai.jp/
 
For Raffle at sacai Hong Kong On Lan Street, sacai Shanghai Reel and sacai Beijing Sanlitunm see detail from the link.
http://sacaixnike.imaginex.com
Raffle starts September 6th 11:00AM and closes September 7th 11:59AM

For Raffle at sacai SKP-S, follow the link below. 
https://skpselect.skp-beijing.com/mode.html?id=521
Raffle will start 16:00 September 6th and will last till 16:00 September 8th.

For Raffle at Shinsegae, follow the link below.
https://m.sivillage.com/event/initEventDetail.siv?event_no=E210806647
Raffle opens at 10AM August 22nd and closes at 12PM August 22nd.

Raffle info for sacai Singapore will be available @club21.
It will be activated from 10:00am to 12:00pm on Sep. 7th.
https://m.sivillage.com/event/initEventDetail.siv?event_no=E210806693

Nike x sacai x CLOT LDWaffle
Nike x sacai x CLOT LDWaffleが9月9日(木)よりNET/ORANGE BLAZE-DP RED-GRN BNが展開。
同日より、RTW capsuleコレクションも展開開始。国内ではsacai THE storeのみで展開。

オンラインで行われる抽選販売については下記の詳細をご確認ください。
※今回、新型コロナウイルス感染症緊急事態宣言発令のため青山店での販売はいたしません。
※オンラインストアのみでの販売となります。

※店舗での購入を楽しみにお待ちいただいておりましたお客様には、ご迷惑をお掛けいたしまして誠に申し訳ございません。　　　

オンラインストアでの販売への抽選応募
9月6日(月) 19:00-翌日7:00の間によりオンラインストア上に表示開始するNike x sacai x CLOT LDWaffle商品ページよりお申込みをお願いいたします。

お申し込み方法や、購入制限等につきましては、サイト掲載の注意事項をよくご確認の上、お申込みをお願いいたします。

https://store.sacai.jp/
#sacai #sacaioffical #sacaithestore

node.text:
@clot x sacai x @nike is a first time three-way partnership and a vision between CLOT co-founder @edcee3000 and sacai founder Chitose Abe.
The special collaboration will see the release of @clot x sacai x @nike LDWaffle "Orange", which will launch on September 9th @juicestore locations world wide and at sacaiTHEstore.
In addition to the LDWaffle launch, collaboration will also feature RTW capsule collection.

Director: Satoshi Ono
DoP/DoV: Kenichi Sonehara
Producer: Ryota Kakihara
Choreographer: Daisuke Omiya @daifresh88 

#sacai #sacaiofficial #clot #clotxsacaixnike
